  "description": "<p>(Fresh-Grad / ORD / No Experience Needed)</p><p></p><p>Fast-Start • Youthful Team</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🔥 Why Join Us?</p><p>•\tHIGH PAYOUT: $3,000–$4,200+/month</p><p>•\tWEEKLY PAYOUT</p><p>•\tSuper fun environment — malls, roadshows, B2B</p><p>•\tYoung, energetic team</p><p>•\tVery beginner-friendly: full training provided</p><p>•\tNo boring office work — all face-to-face, engaging, and active</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>🎉 What You’ll Be Doing</p><p>•\tRepresent brands at events, malls, roadshows, and B2B</p><p>•\tPresent active campaigns to potential customers</p><p>•\tCreate a fun, hype, engaging experience for customers</p><p>•\tConvert customer interest into sales</p><p>•\tWork closely with a youthful, high-energy team</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>💰 Earnings & Benefits</p><p>•\tWeekly payouts available</p><p>•\tHigh commissions</p><p>•\tFast career progression</p><p>•\tSupportive leaders & step-by-step training</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>✨ We’re Looking For:</p><p>•\tOutgoing, energetic, and confident individuals</p><p>•\tEnjoys talking to people</p><p>•\tTeam player who loves a fun, young environment</p><p>•\tNo experience required — we’ll train you!</p><p></p><p>⸻</p><p></p><p>📩 Ready to Join?</p><p>Apply now !</p>",
